OL,3,CRecycling centre staff fear acid burns
OL,4,Cafter aggression from the public
OL,6,F''My first thought was 'Am I
OL,7,Fburning?'. I was just looking at my
OL,8,Fclothes looking for any burns I just
OL,9,Fthought it was like an acid type
OL,10,Fattack. I was just totally in shock.''
OL,12,FStaff at Cornwall's household waste
OL,13,Fand recycling centres (HWRC) have
OL,14,Frevealed the abuse and aggression they
OL,15,Fhave experienced for simply doing
OL,16,Ftheir jobs.
