OL,3,CRecycling centre staff fear acid burns
OL,4,Cafter aggression from the public
OL,6,FSupervisor Simon Collett endured a
OL,7,Fharrowing attack in which he told a
OL,8,Fvisitor to the site in Lanivet near
OL,9,FBodmin they could not bring in trade
OL,10,Fwaste.
OL,12,FThey became angry and threw an unknown
OL,13,Fliquid into his face.
OL,15,FHe says it's had a lasting impact on
OL,16,Fhim: "I'm just waiting for the next
OL,17,Fattack or if I'm going to be
OL,18,Fphysically assaulted."
