OL,3,CRecycling centre staff fear acid burns
OL,4,Cafter aggression from the public
OL,6,F"The flashbacks, the aftermath of this
OL,7,Fhorrible unprovoked attack. It was a
OL,8,Fcowardly attack. Just no need for it."
OL,10,FHis colleague James Maughan who worked
OL,11,Fat recycling centres in East Cornwall
OL,12,Fsays he's experienced around 50
OL,13,Fincidents in 5 years.
OL,15,FIn one he was threatened by a man who
OL,16,Ftold him he 'would have his throat
OL,17,Fripped out'. He found it so
OL,18,Ftraumatising he's had to change jobs
OL,19,Faway from the public.
