OL,3,CRecycling centre staff fear acid burns
OL,4,Cafter aggression from the public
OL,6,FHe said: "He became incredibly
OL,7,Faggressive, with threats of violence.
OL,8,FI also thought he was going to arrange
OL,9,Fto have me followed home and
OL,10,Fsubsequently make threats to my
OL,11,Ffamily."
OL,13,FSUEZ is the company that operates the
OL,14,Fwaste facilities for Cornwall Council.
OL,15,FIt has launched a campaign called 'We
OL,16,FRefuse Abuse' with a film to raise
OL,17,Fawareness and stop aggression towards
OL,18,Fstaff at its waste centres and against
OL,19,Fcollection crews.
