OL,6,FThe council is backing the campaign
OL,7,Fand says violent incidents like these
OL,8,Fare reported to police.
OL,10,FJohn Scanlon, CEO of SUEZ, said: "A
OL,11,Fvery small minority of aggressive
OL,12,Findividuals have caused members of our
OL,13,Fteam enormous stress and upset and we
OL,14,Fwant to ensure this upward trend in
OL,15,Fverbal and physical assaults does not
OL,16,Fcontinue."
